Package: trackr
Type: Package
Title: Track Progress and Forecast Targets for WDI Indicators
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rossana Tatulli
Maintainer: Rossana Tatulli <rtatulli@worldbank.org>
Description: Calculates progress scores and projects future targets for any indicator of interest. Users can choose their preferred methods and parameters to evaluate and project country performance. Depending on the settings, the package returns two to six data frames summarizing percentile-based and speed-based scores, along with historical and projected indicator trajectories under different assumptions.
